call-for-presenters.name: Call for Presenters
call-for-presenters.desc: We're gearing up for the first South-East Asia Angular conference and you can help make it a memorable one by participating as a speaker. Be part of the Angular community today!

speaker-nomination.name: Nominate a Speaker
speaker-nomination.desc: There will always be that few talented and brilliant people we look up to. Why not take this chance to get them to share their knowledge with the bigger community at NG-MY 2019?

speaker-training.name: Feb 23 | Speaker Training
speaker-training.desc: Are you wondering if you can speak at a tech conference / meetup or whether your topics are interesting enough? This 1 day exclusive event will be held to answer your questions. Interested? Fill up the form & get invite!

call-for-sponsors.name: Call for Sponsors
call-for-sponsors.desc: Interested to become one of the sponsors for the very first South-East Asia Angular conference? Contact us today and be part of this vibrant community in making NG-MY 2019 a success.

sponsor-referral.name: Refer a Sponsor
sponsor-referral.desc: We love to increase our network with companies and you definitely can help us with that. Refer a sponsor to us, win a free ticket and make NG-MY 2019 a success.

scholarship.name: Scholarship
scholarship.desc: Scholarship application open now till April 30.

ticket-giveaways.name: Guess the logo contest
ticket-giveaways.desc: 2 free NG-MY 2019 tickets up for grabs! All you have to do is to participate in our contest! Closing date is 26th Ap.
